{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and sometimes I find myself even today using it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I find when-- when crowd gathered and everybody is so curious over things, I-- I-- I-- I make sure I'm out of there, until today.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't want to be part of a crowd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I try to be out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Don't want to be caught up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It-- maybe it's left over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I watch people, like, they see an incident on the freeway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They see a burning building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They want to stand around and watch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I want to be out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I'll try anything to get away from those places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I guess it's-- it's like a trigger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Lots of things will-- will trigger remembrances and incidents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I know I was young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I said, I was really never with them from the time-- actually, from the beginning of the ghetto I was never really with anybody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was strictly by myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I slept with my mother during those years, except for the ghetto when I was up on the-- on-- on the-- on the-- on the attic and-- and later on in the camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was working and just sleeping with my mother, and the men were separate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was really never together with my family once we were all separated after that bunker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was strictly on my own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I guess it happened in 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I guess the-- the Germans were starting to lose the war, but I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't-- [LAUGHS] I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All I know is that one day, we were all marched, and we were put on those cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
